snippet.title: Skyward Dream — Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2776230/Skyward_Dream/
Embark on a dream journey in "Skyward Dream," a first-person atmospheric platforming adventure set within the surreal landscapes of dreams. Traverse floating islands and discover the meaning of every jump. "Skyward Dream" invites you to leap into a world where reality blurs and aspirations take flight.
